data.description: BACK ON MARKET at absolutely NO FAULT TO SELLER! Serous buyers will only be accepted!   This beautiful home is truly a must see! Property has been immaculately maintained! Located on a large lot in Patriot Landing Community, just minutes away from Shaw Airforce Base! Built in 2010, this home offers a combination of a closed floor plan with open concepts!  Highlights of this property include:  Newly installed luxury vinyl plank flooring in foyer, powder-room, walkways,  and throughout the eat-in kitchen! Freshly painted interior. This unique floorplan includes a formal living room, dining room, and family room. Kitchen features Cherrywood cabinets, granite countertops, large walk-in pantry, and a built in desk area! All 4 bedrooms are spacious and contain ceiling fans and walk-in closets. Laundry room on 2nd floor. Large owner's suite features garden tub, separate shower, and oversized walk-in closet! 4th bedroom is uniquely designed featuring an open-walkway concept and nook area! HUGE flat backyard is completely fenced and includes irrigation system. BRAND NEW ROOF installed in late 2022.
